# Pycollect

Pycollect can do many things. Things like finding information about your collection of video games to everything you can think about.

##Everything?

Pycollect was made with a plugin architecture in mind. Which means that you can write your own plugin and pycollect will be able to do it.

## How to use

You simple have to install it by cloning this repository

	git clone https://github.com/numkem/pycollect
	cd pycollect
	python2 setup.py

Than you can run the script by using the `pycollect` command.

## Plugins

### List

So far pycollect has support for these websites:
* vgcollect